export function getFieldSpecification() {

    { "fieldLength": "255", "mandatory": false, "controlType": "textarea", "idsName": "IDS_DESCRIPTION", "dataField": "sdescription", "width": "400px", "mandatoryLabel": "IDS_ENTER", "ndesigncomponentcode": 2 },

    { "fieldLength": "100", "mandatory": true, "controlType": "textbox", "idsName": "IDS_REASON", "dataField": "sreason", "width": "200px", "mandatoryLabel": "IDS_ENTER", "ndesigncomponentcode": 1 },
    { "fieldLength": "255", "mandatory": false, "controlType": "textarea", "idsName": "IDS_DESCRIPTION", "dataField": "sdescription", "width": "400px", "mandatoryLabel": "IDS_ENTER", "ndesigncomponentcode": 2 }
    ]);

    screenMap.set("ProjectType", [{ "fieldLength": "NA", "dataField": "nprojecttypecode", "mandatory": false, "controlType": "NA" },
    { "fieldLength": "50", "mandatory": true, "controlType": "textbox", "idsName": "IDS_PROJECTTYPE", "dataField": "sprojecttypename", "jsonObjectName": "jsondata", "width": "200px", "mandatoryLabel": "IDS_ENTER", "ndesigncomponentcode": 1 },
